Description: A comprehensive R package providing an end-to-end graphical user interface 
    and reproducible R Markdown workflows for multi-omics data analysis. MultiScholaR 
    supports proteomics, metabolomics, lipidomics, and integrative 
    multi-omics analyses with automated parameter optimization, quality control, 
    differential expression analysis, and pathway enrichment. The package emphasizes 
    transparency and education, providing well-documented workflows that enable 
    researchers to understand and adapt analytical methods while ensuring reproducibility 
    through standardized, citable workflows.
